13. useRef Hook
Definition: Access DOM elements directly.
Example
JSX
const inputRef = useRef();

<input ref={inputRef}/>
Real-world Example
Auto-focus Search Box.
14. useMemo Hook
Definition: Optimizes expensive calculations.
Example
JSX
const result = useMemo(()=>{
 return calculateData();
},[]);
Real-world Example
Large E-commerce Product Filtering.
15. useCallback Hook
Definition: Memoizes functions.
Example
JSX
const handleClick = useCallback(()=>{
 console.log("Clicked");
},[]);
Real-world Example
Large Dashboard Applications.
